{"type":"message","id":"3a085918","parentId":"1e95a4a1","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:30:09.414Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:1b826305-b255-4d80-b282-f51494c67425 goodnight-story] FIRST: Read /root/.openclaw/workspace/CRON-CONTEXT.md for context. Send a bedtime story to group via message(action=send, channel=telegram, target=-1003606834639). Story: real historical event or powerful life lesson, 8-12 lines, simple language, something people genuinely love. End with goodnight wish. Search the web for a compelling true story if needed. If fails, message Nemesis at target=7924461837.\nCurrent time: Friday, April 10th, 2026 - 4:30 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-10 16:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775838609399}}
